{"tid":619972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣傳港獨　阻止赤教　保我國土　衛我民族　港生動源　招募義工","createTime":"2018-04-07T07:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T00:13:27.000Z","uid":47714,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bda93f2817c8f5e9aa4a26f0c3d4266ec41d29c5","tid":619972,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studentlocalism/photos/a.1034067780001639.1073741828.1033983876676696/1891126070962468/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudentlocalism%2Fphotos%2Fa.1034067780001639.1073741828.1033983876676696%2F1891126070962468%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=858778c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studentlocalism/photos/a.1034067780001639.1073741828.1033983876676696/1891126070962468/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【學生動源現正招募義工團】<br />\n<br />\n學生動源未來將會繼續宣傳香港獨立，而林鄭月娥就任後勢必重推國民教育，身為學生阻止國民教育絕對責無旁貸，故此需要大量人手。要成為義工，你必須是香港學生並符合以下條件：<br />\n<br />\n1.支持香港獨立<br />\n2.支持一切有效的抗爭模式<br />\n3.願意付出汗水和私人時間<br />\n4.擁有捍衛香港民族未來的決心<br />\n<br />\n學生動源義工團申請表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/0aTVtBYp1DcWg7Gv2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F0aTVtBYp1DcWg7Gv2&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ea19d9c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/0aTVtBYp1DcWg7Gv2</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n學生動源PayPal自由定額資助： <a href=\"http://paypal.me/StudentlocalismHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.me%2FStudentlocalismHK&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=39c054bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">paypal.me/StudentlocalismHK</a><br />\n<br />\n學生動源Telegram頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/studentlocalism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstudentlocalism&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=08718b31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/studentlocalism</a><br />\n<br />\n學生動源Instagram Channel：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/studentlocalism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstudentlocalism%2F&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9b728920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/studentlocalism/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/fzPwX7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfzPwX7&h=f4a34463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b523642899317058a547806b18b895cd34146cfe","tid":619972,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/151744_86c12396febfec6e23e9c381fc6edd0e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F151744_86c12396febfec6e23e9c381fc6edd0e.gif&h=3faaf7ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13fbc880ea49fa3423573e61cad347a92746b4c8","tid":619972,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87b035289838ee1e2c0ba230d853e0d06fceca05","tid":619972,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afb354a573bece5f3661ac5f7f46a2b5f1961baf","tid":619972,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  閱"},{"pid":"2740b1ae27ff62ea4e82c1e4b00f449ebf81dc37","tid":619972,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:46:45.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"44aa1ff6bbe667567d5c8643d3311ec3fdf31070","tid":619972,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43242ebabcf5d8a9424600253edd1535cd9d7f53","tid":619